TotalVinPowABS Y: Current flowing into mirrors due to all input pulses
BranchVDDPowABs Y: Power From VDD for both branches
BranchCapRefAbs Y: Power to both Caps for reset
VDDPowAbs Y: VDD Power Abs (Branches and cap ref and input current and comparator)
WeightInverters Y: Inverters for a single weight signal  multiplied by 45

BranchVDDPowABs Y: Neither comparator nor weights should really be counted.
